gov.nih.nlm.ling.graph

Class DummyNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.ling.graph.DummyNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Node

    public class DummyNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements Node
    Represents a dummy node, which can be used to represent units that go beyond textual units, such as documents, sentences, quotations, etc. This is expected to be mostly useful for discourse processing.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
